commit 6768604566ffda5fb63fa9541a757f1ea768a27b
Author: Maxim Milakov <mmilakov@nvidia.com>
Date:   Wed Feb 24 03:33:12 2021 -0800

    Batch compression/decompression test for Snappy added
---
 tests/test_snappy_batch_c_api.c | 252 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
